race.comment: WOWZINO (3) boasts a win over this nine-furlong journey and has placed two of three starts around this circuit. Will be at peak fitness for this and should be right there at the business end. ROAD TO PARADISE (10) got the chocolates at the latest effort and will have derived a stack of confidence from that breakthrough victory. Can go back-to-back without surprising. THROTTLE RESPONSE (6) hails from the champion Waller barn and looks to be working up to another victory. Top-three contender. KAFFIR LILY (9) is a last-start winner who get in very well at the weights with the claim. Has to be included. BIG TICKET BOY (2) draws the inside alley and may make his presence felt.
